<section class="intro">
    <h2>Welcome to the USF Parking Monitor</h2>
    <p>
        This prototype web application is designed to help students, faculty, and staff view available parking spaces across the USF campus in real time.
        While real-time data integration is a future enhancement, this version presents the foundational structure for CRUD operations and data display.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <h3>Key Features (Planned)</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>🔄 Live updates on parking availability</li>
        <li>📍 Parking lot zones and names</li>
        <li>📊 Data visualization for parking trends</li>
        <li>🛠️ Admin dashboard for managing lot info</li>
    </ul>
</section>